    "@type": "Question",
    "name": "Can we use a prenup to determine child custody?",
    "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "No. A prenup only has to do with property, not children. You should avoid including any language about custody of children or child support in your prenuptial agreement."
